    Sort and Re-order/Sort by and Display order menu

    The order shown in the portal
      • Urgency
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Date crated
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Date published (DSC)
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Date of last agent reply
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Date of last user reply
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Widget type
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Widget description
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Desired sizes
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Manufacturing date
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Reason for cancellation
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Reason for complaint
        • Ascending
        • Descending
      • Suggested actions
        • Ascending
        • Descending
